WEBVTT

01:33.468 --> 01:35.812
Ah, little scoundrel.

01:37.431 --> 01:40.150
There you are.
You are a bad boy.

01:40.142 --> 01:44.067
Come on.
Hop on.

01:44.146 --> 01:46.615
Like you always do.

01:57.909 --> 02:01.209
Holy sacraments!
You'll kill yourself!

02:19.264 --> 02:22.143
Only God knows how much
I loved you.

02:42.537 --> 02:45.211
- Someone has died.
- Huh-uh.

02:45.290 --> 02:49.921
- It's Pentecost.
- No no, it must be a very big fish

02:50.003 --> 02:53.098
if they are ringing
the cathedral bells.

02:54.383 --> 02:57.136
Florentino, lay down.

02:59.012 --> 03:00.980
Let's do it again.

03:01.056 --> 03:03.104
Please?

03:03.183 --> 03:06.813
Tolling like that must
be for a governor at least.

03:06.895 --> 03:09.444
Or...

03:09.523 --> 03:11.651
What?

03:14.778 --> 03:16.780
What is it?

03:31.461 --> 03:35.887
America, you must
go back to college.

03:37.426 --> 03:40.145
My driver will take you.
There is something I have to do.

03:42.681 --> 03:45.275
My deepest
sympathy.

03:46.435 --> 03:48.984
Your father
was a saint.

03:54.776 --> 03:57.780
- My condolences.
- I'm so sorry.

03:58.780 --> 04:00.498
We would still
have cholera

04:00.574 --> 04:03.794
if it had not
been for him.

04:03.869 --> 04:05.837
My sympathies,
Mrs. Urbino.

04:15.630 --> 04:18.382
Let's go, Mom.

04:24.097 --> 04:27.021
- See you all later, gentlemen.
- See you later.

04:27.100 --> 04:29.979
Mama, I'll stay
if you want me to.

04:55.045 --> 04:58.015
Fermina, I have waited

04:58.089 --> 05:00.808
for this opportunity
for 51 years,

05:00.884 --> 05:02.932
nine months
and four days.

05:05.347 --> 05:08.396
That is how long
I have loved you,

05:08.475 --> 05:11.069
from the first moment
I cast eyes on you until now.

05:13.021 --> 05:15.399
I repeat
to you once again

05:15.482 --> 05:19.328
my vow
of eternal fidelity

05:19.402 --> 05:22.030
and everlasting love.

05:24.866 --> 05:27.039
Florentino Ariza...

05:29.913 --> 05:32.166
get out of here!

05:35.085 --> 05:36.962
Get out!

05:38.880 --> 05:42.384
And don't show your face again for
the years of life that are left to you.

05:45.887 --> 05:48.891
And I hope there are
very few of them.

07:18.396 --> 07:21.320
Florentino Ariza!

07:27.489 --> 07:28.741
Florentino!

07:31.242 --> 07:32.835
Ah!

07:32.827 --> 07:35.330
- That's not a telegram, Carlos.
- Come on, come on.

07:35.330 --> 07:38.880
Deliver this, please,
to Sefior Lorenzo Daza.

07:39.876 --> 07:42.425
Old house,
Park of Evangels.

07:42.504 --> 07:45.348
New in town,
a rough diamond.

07:45.423 --> 07:48.848
Owns mules,
lots of mules.

07:48.843 --> 07:50.971
Thank you, Lotario.

07:55.392 --> 07:57.144
Thank you.

07:58.645 --> 08:02.616
Yes yes, I'm coming.
I'm coming.

08:12.575 --> 08:14.828
Last time you charged me
400 gold pesos,

08:14.911 --> 08:18.085
that's double what I paid for this
whole abbey cloister-- what?!

08:18.164 --> 08:20.713
Sefior Lorenzo Daza.

08:20.709 --> 08:22.928
Yes.

08:27.549 --> 08:30.348
Oh, good news.
Good news!

08:32.386 --> 08:34.640
No reply-

08:34.722 --> 08:36.645
Look at the shape
of the letter.

08:36.725 --> 08:38.773
Not “U" but “A.”

08:38.852 --> 08:40.900
M-me--

08:40.979 --> 08:44.734
M-m--me--

08:44.816 --> 08:46.443
mis--

08:46.526 --> 08:49.245
mist--

08:49.320 --> 08:51.948
mistook--

08:52.032 --> 08:54.410
Sefior, Sefior!

08:54.409 --> 08:58.004
Ta k-- mistook--

08:58.079 --> 09:00.628
