09:00.707 --> 09:02.675
Good.
Good.

09:02.751 --> 09:04.424
Very good.

09:09.591 --> 09:12.435
Mistook, mistake,

09:12.510 --> 09:14.057
mistaken.

09:14.137 --> 09:17.482
- What do you want?
- Look, I didn't do anything.

09:30.195 --> 09:32.618
Don't you greet
your mother?

09:35.366 --> 09:37.243
Florentino,
have you eaten?

09:37.327 --> 09:39.455
Have you eaten?

09:47.796 --> 09:49.264
“Fermina Daza,

09:49.339 --> 09:51.137
for I have learned

09:51.132 --> 09:54.807
that is your majestic

09:54.803 --> 09:58.649
immortal name.

09:58.723 --> 10:01.021
I write
this very short note

10:01.101 --> 10:04.480
in order
to let you know...

10:05.897 --> 10:08.320
that I love you.”

10:08.316 --> 10:10.739
- You haven't been to bed.
- Shh!

10:10.819 --> 10:12.287
- Are you ill?
- No.

10:12.362 --> 10:14.364
You are so pale, my son.
Are you sure?

10:14.447 --> 10:16.996
- I'm not ill.
- Let me feel your head.

10:16.991 --> 10:19.744
Let me feel your head.

10:19.828 --> 10:22.672
What are you writing,
a book?

10:22.664 --> 10:25.042
No, a letter.

10:25.125 --> 10:28.925
All these pages,
and they're just one letter.

10:29.003 --> 10:30.880
But what kind of a letter?

10:32.173 --> 10:34.471
Holy Mother.

10:37.720 --> 10:40.064
It is a love letter.

10:40.140 --> 10:43.269
Oh, my son,
who is she?

10:43.351 --> 10:45.945
Her name is...

10:47.772 --> 10:49.695
Fermina Daza.

10:49.774 --> 10:51.697
They're new in town.

10:51.693 --> 10:54.412
Her mother is dead.
Her father owns mules.

10:54.487 --> 10:58.708
And, Mama, I have discovered
the reason for my existence.

10:58.783 --> 11:01.002
Don't talk such
nonsense, my son.

11:01.077 --> 11:02.454
That's it!

11:02.537 --> 11:04.710
Come on, come on,
come on.

11:04.706 --> 11:06.708
But there is money in mules.

11:08.376 --> 11:10.299
Does Fermina Daza
return your love?

11:10.378 --> 11:11.971
“L've discovered...”

11:12.046 --> 11:13.719
I don't know.
We haven't spoken.

11:13.715 --> 11:15.717
That's why I'm writing
the letter.

11:15.717 --> 11:18.140
If I can find the opportunity,
I'll give it to her,

11:18.219 --> 11:20.062
but she's always
with her aunt.

11:20.138 --> 11:24.143
