12:02.430 --> 12:04.148
Eh-hh.

12:28.164 --> 12:30.383
- Let me stand next to her.
- No!

12:35.713 --> 12:37.590
Sefiorita Daza,

12:37.674 --> 12:39.972
all I ask is that you accept
a letter from me.

12:39.968 --> 12:41.936
- Not now.
- When?

12:42.011 --> 12:44.184
Afterwards.

12:46.099 --> 12:47.942
Corpus Christi.

12:50.144 --> 12:51.942
