- Amen.

13:12.959 --> 13:15.178
Welcome, Fernando!

13:18.631 --> 13:21.100
Papa, I'm going
to wish

13:21.175 --> 13:23.598
Mother Superior
a happy Christmas.

13:28.766 --> 13:31.690
This is the greatest moment
in my life.

13:31.769 --> 13:33.521
Give it to me.

13:33.521 --> 13:35.865
It was very long.
I made it shorter.

13:37.442 --> 13:39.365
Wait!

13:39.360 --> 13:41.408
It's a flower
of promising.

13:41.487 --> 13:43.615
Go.

13:43.698 --> 13:47.123
And don't see me again
until you hear from me.

14:16.564 --> 14:19.784
My Holy Mother.
My Holy Mother.

14:19.859 --> 14:22.112
It is cholera, my son.
It is cholera.

14:22.195 --> 14:23.868
- No, Mama.
- My son!

14:23.946 --> 14:27.041
I gave her the letter.

14:30.119 --> 14:32.622
Now I must wait
for her reply.

14:32.705 --> 14:36.255
Yeah.
Then enjoy your pain.

14:36.334 --> 14:39.838
Take advantage of it now
while you are young.

14:39.921 --> 14:43.425
And suffer, my son,
suffer all you can,

14:43.424 --> 14:46.394
because these things don't
last your whole life.

14:48.888 --> 14:51.391
May she answer soon.

14:53.267 --> 14:55.269
She won't.

15:06.114 --> 15:09.869
Florentino!

15:11.452 --> 15:12.999
What the hell
you are doing?

15:14.455 --> 15:16.799
It's not an American ship,
it's British.

15:16.874 --> 15:19.798
It's the mail from Liverpool.
British.

15:22.004 --> 15:23.881
Come here.

15:27.468 --> 15:30.563
What is wrong with you?
This isn't love.

15:30.638 --> 15:33.608
It's madness.
Give me, give me.

15:34.892 --> 15:36.360
Up LIP "P "P-

15:37.520 --> 15:39.898
No, wait wait.

15:42.984 --> 15:44.907
<i>“OW! go'</i>

