What is wrong
with you?

15:56.873 --> 15:59.171
You need to take
your mind off her.

15:59.250 --> 16:01.298
Come with me
to the whorehouse if--

16:14.891 --> 16:16.734
Yes?

16:16.809 --> 16:19.187
Oh, how much is it
to send a telegram

16:19.270 --> 16:20.863
to the village
of Piedras de Moler?

16:22.440 --> 16:24.534
- Piedras de Moler?
- Uh-huh.

16:26.819 --> 16:29.163
Uh... let me see.

16:32.074 --> 16:34.168
It's--
it's not on our list.

16:34.243 --> 16:37.713
