- Th-- then--

16:45.922 --> 16:48.220
good day to you.

16:55.306 --> 16:56.307
Sefiorita!

17:11.739 --> 17:14.538
“Dear Florentino Ariza...

17:14.617 --> 17:16.290
I am sorry that I have

17:16.368 --> 17:19.167
made you wait so long
for my reply.

17:19.247 --> 17:21.590
I ask your forgiveness.

17:21.665 --> 17:24.589
Please, write to me
again soon.”

17:28.714 --> 17:31.217
“Crowned goddess, I enclose

17:31.300 --> 17:33.394
what I know is
a worthless memento.

17:33.469 --> 17:37.269
I also write this verse
in honor of my love for you.”

17:40.601 --> 17:43.024
“I think of you every moment.

17:43.104 --> 17:46.950
Now that spring is here,
thoughts of you fill me with life.

17:48.109 --> 17:49.952
I will love you forever.

17:49.944 --> 17:51.912
Forever.”

18:35.281 --> 18:37.249
Shh-hhh.

18:44.457 --> 18:46.380
Shhh.

19:11.067 --> 19:14.196
- It's him.
- Of course it's him.

19:18.282 --> 19:20.705
- Sefiorita Escoléstica?
- Shhh.

19:20.701 --> 19:22.874
Sefiorita Escoléstica,

19:22.953 --> 19:26.833
please turn apart so I can talk
privately to the young lady.

19:26.916 --> 19:29.339
I have something important
to ask her.

19:29.418 --> 19:32.217
What impertinence!

19:32.213 --> 19:35.057
There's nothing that has to do with her
that I cannot hear.

19:36.384 --> 19:38.057
Then I will not
say anything.

19:38.135 --> 19:39.887
But I warn you,

19:39.887 --> 19:42.561
you will be responsible
for the consequences.

19:47.311 --> 19:50.440
- Fermina Daza.
- I am here.

19:50.523 --> 19:52.571
We've written
too many letters

19:52.566 --> 19:54.819
and too much time
has passed.

19:54.902 --> 19:57.576
So now...

19:57.655 --> 20:00.329
crowned goddess,

20:00.408 --> 20:02.456
I make this vow.

20:02.535 --> 20:05.505
I swear to you
my eternal fidelity

20:05.579 --> 20:08.082
and everlasting love,

20:08.082 --> 20:10.926
and I ask in all humility

20:11.001 --> 20:15.131
to do me the great honor
of marrying me.

20:16.424 --> 20:18.552
You--

20:18.634 --> 20:21.763
you must give me time.

20:21.762 --> 20:24.231
Fermina, say yes!

20:24.306 --> 20:27.276
Fermina, I may not be married,
but I know about love.

20:27.351 --> 20:28.944
Even if you're
dying of fear,

20:28.936 --> 20:31.314
even if you are sorry later,
because whatever you do,

20:31.397 --> 20:33.946
you will be sorry
all the rest of your life if you say no.

20:34.024 --> 20:36.072
Believe me, I know
what I'm talking about.

20:47.455 --> 20:49.298
Yes, very well.

20:49.290 --> 20:51.634
I will marry you

20:51.625 --> 20:54.003
if you-- if you promise
not to make me eat

20:54.086 --> 20:55.838
eggplant.

21:05.931 --> 21:07.808
Who is he?
Who is he?

21:07.892 --> 21:09.735
Who is he?

21:12.104 --> 21:14.106
Who is this
Florentino Ariza?

21:14.190 --> 21:15.863
Huh?

21:15.941 --> 21:18.990
And Mother Superior
says that you write letters to him?

21:18.986 --> 21:21.409
And you-- you!

21:21.489 --> 21:23.617
You are to blame.

21:39.423 --> 21:41.721
No!

21:41.801 --> 21:44.395
Aunt!

21:53.729 --> 21:57.779
No!

22:12.998 --> 22:15.626
Daughter, daughter,
listen to your father.

22:15.709 --> 22:18.212
Listen to your father.
Everything I do,

22:18.295 --> 22:20.263
I do it because--

22:20.339 --> 22:21.966
because I--

22:22.049 --> 22:24.598
okay, I'll try.
I'll try, but--

22:24.677 --> 22:28.147
but I have to-- I have to ex--
I have to explain myself.

22:28.222 --> 22:31.647
I have to explain myself.
It's difficult because I'm a plain man.

22:35.437 --> 22:37.439
But ever since
your mother died,

22:37.523 --> 22:39.571
you've been--

22:39.567 --> 22:41.740
you've been...

22:41.735 --> 22:44.079
a daughter--
a daughter is a jewel.

22:44.071 --> 22:47.075
Is a jewel. I'm--
I'm-- I'm a rough diamond, but you're--

22:47.074 --> 22:50.419
