I don't work for me.

22:52.788 --> 22:55.917
We didn't come here for me.
We came here for you.

22:55.916 --> 22:58.089
For you!

22:58.085 --> 23:00.213
But you don't know how--
just how beautiful you are.

23:00.296 --> 23:01.923
You-you-you--
you're-- you're--

23:02.006 --> 23:05.556
you're much too beautiful
to marry a telegraph operator.

23:08.345 --> 23:10.848
We have bigger fish to fry,
and believe me-- believe me,

23:10.931 --> 23:14.606
at your age,
love is an illusion.

23:19.273 --> 23:20.775
Christ, by Christ I swear,

23:20.774 --> 23:23.368
I swear,
I swear to Christ--

23:47.343 --> 23:49.437
Good morning,
good morning.

23:52.681 --> 23:55.810
You and I must talk--
man to man.

24:02.608 --> 24:04.110
Ahhhh.

24:04.193 --> 24:07.618
When my wife died
I set myself one goal.

24:07.696 --> 24:09.664
One goal--

24:09.740 --> 24:12.664
to turn my daughter
into a great lady.

24:12.743 --> 24:16.373
Now that's-- that's a long road
to travel for a mule trader.

24:16.455 --> 24:18.799
I've never had a drink
this early in the morning.

24:18.874 --> 24:21.923
Better start now.
You're going to need it.

24:27.007 --> 24:29.305
I came to this town
because...

24:29.385 --> 24:32.138
well, here was the possibility
of a grand marriage.

24:32.221 --> 24:35.100
Then an unforeseen
obstacle

24:35.182 --> 24:38.026
