fought for with my life...

24:39.019 --> 24:41.113
YOu.

24:42.856 --> 24:45.075
So I've come to make
a polite request.

24:47.152 --> 24:49.120
Get out of our way.

24:49.196 --> 24:51.369
Have you spoken to her?

24:51.365 --> 24:53.709
None of that. None of that.
This is a matter for men

24:53.701 --> 24:56.045
and it will be decided
by men.

24:57.997 --> 24:59.840
