civil war might.

30:36.043 --> 30:38.216
And there is the disease

30:38.211 --> 30:41.590
that comes between
the burst of bloodshed,

30:41.673 --> 30:44.722
the deadly choking embrace
of cholera.

30:44.718 --> 30:49.098
